utils

Class TTEQueue

  • java.lang.Object
    • utils.TTEQueue

  • public class TTEQueue
extends java.lang.Object
    A singleton queue that stores data read by VeniceReader objects and provide it for VeniceWriter objects, with delaying items by use of the timestamp.

    The data have to be TTE items. They will be provided in the order of their timestamp.

    See Also:
    DelayQueue, TTE
